pageTitle: Practice will be this Sunday (April 14th), Saturdays Practice Postponed Due to Weather – Kalamazoo Speedway
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {19968=Due to the forecast for mixed rain & snow for Saturday as well as a high of only 40 degree’s,  we have postponed Saturdays Practice & will be having Open Practice this Sunday, April 14th, from 1-5PM.  Pit gates will open at noon, grandstands are free and pit passes are $20.  The water still is not on, so the concessions or the restrooms will not be open yet., 31325=Get in touch! 269-692-2423 | info@kalamazoospeedway.com}
